python-opencl aims at being an easy to use Python wrapper around the OpenCL.

It is licensed under the GPLv3 or any later version. The license information
can be found in the file named COPYING.

python-opencl websites of interests include:

- Homepage at http://python-opencl.next-touch.com/
- Project page at http://gitorious.org/python-opencl
- ML at https://listes.lautre.net/cgi-bin/mailman/listinfo/python-opencl
